*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&  Include           ZECGC_CUST_AGEING_F01
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
* ECGC Customer Ageing Report - Subroutines (Performance Optimized)
*
* WHAT WAS OPTIMIZED vs Reference ZR2RR071_CUSTOMER_AGEING:
*  1. NET_DUE_DATE_GET - RETAINED (complex SAP payment term logic,
*     handles rebzg/shkzg/koart - cannot be safely simplified)
*  2. FIMA_DAYS_AND_MONTHS_AND_YEARS - REPLACED with ABAP date math
*     (safe: we only need day difference, date subtraction is identical)
*  3. UKM_MALUSLIST_PROCESSING - batched (single call for ALL partners
*     instead of one per customer)
*  4. FIELD-SYMBOLS in every LOOP and READ TABLE (no data copy)
*  5. BINARY SEARCH on every READ TABLE with proper preceding SORT
*  6. Eliminated gt_fagl1/gt_fagl2 redundant copy loops
*  7. Bucket limits converted to integer once (gv_c1..gv_c5)
*  8. Group entity elimination conditional on company code >= 5000
*     (1010 and 1020 process all customers without elimination)
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*


*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      Form  GET_DATA
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM get_data .

  DATA: lv_bukrs_num TYPE i.

* Convert bucket limits to integer once
  gv_c1 = p_c1.
  gv_c2 = p_c2.
  gv_c3 = p_c3.
  gv_c4 = p_c4.
  gv_c5 = p_c5.

  PERFORM build_elimination_list.
  PERFORM fetch_kna1.

* Group entity elimination applies ONLY for company code >= 5000
* (1010 and 1020 process all customers normally without elimination)
  lv_bukrs_num = s_bukrs-low.
  IF lv_bukrs_num >= 5000.
    PERFORM eliminate_group_entities.
  ENDIF.

  PERFORM fetch_bsad.
  PERFORM fetch_bsid.
  PERFORM merge_data.
  PERFORM move_to_final.
  PERFORM adjust_advance_in_summary.
  PERFORM fetch_credit_data_batch.
  PERFORM display_output.

ENDFORM.


*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      Form  BUILD_ELIMINATION_LIST
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
